The paper discusses the design and implementation of a knowledge-oriented information system for scientific research and development support. It focuses on the creation and use of an ontological knowledge base for research fellow publications, which suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the Information Retrieval (cs.IR), Digital Libraries (cs.DL), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), Software Engineering (cs.SE), or Databases (cs.DB) sub-categories.
